### ✅ Report a New Crisis
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seekerId": 1,
  "crisisType": "Depression",
  "description": "Feeling extremely low and hopeless",
  "priority": 3
}

### ✅ Assign a Counselor to a Crisis
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "crisisId": 1,
  "counselorId": 2
}

### ✅ Update Crisis Status
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "crisisId": 1,
  "status": "Resolved",
  "resolvedAt": "2025-02-23T12:00:00Z"
}

### ✅ Delete a Crisis
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/1

### ✅ Log a Crisis Call
POST http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/calls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "crisisId": 1,
  "callerId": 2,
  "callStart": "2025-02-23T10:30:00Z",
  "callType": "Phone"
}

### ✅ Delete a Crisis Call
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/crisis/calls/1

